# Launcher home (frozen)

Read **`docs/specs/LAUNCHER_HOME_CONSTRAINTS.md`** before changing home UI, panel size, or list chrome.  
Panel positioning: **`docs/specs/LAUNCHER_PANEL_CONSTRAINTS.md`**.  
Navigation / detail exit / shortcuts: **`docs/specs/UX_BEHAVIOR_RULES.md`**, open issues in **`docs/qa/LAUNCHER_NAVIGATION_AUDIT.md`**.

## Empty-query home shows ONLY

- **Open Apps** section — all running apps, no `+N more` row.

## Do NOT restore without a new ADR

- Setup / 开始使用 rows or `SetupHomeProvider` on home
- Recent / 最近, Continue / 继续, Create / 创建 sections
- Auto-present onboarding wizard
- Gray background on every idle list row

## Panel

- Default **720 × 680 pt**, upper-third (`panelVerticalBias` 0.68).
- Tokens: `LauncherChromeTokens.swift`.
- Positioning + in-panel layout: **`docs/specs/LAUNCHER_PANEL_CONSTRAINTS.md`** — no `anchorPoint` on root; no full-width `wantsLayer`; use `LauncherPanel.position(on:)` and child-chrome helpers.

## Where features go instead

- Search, module prefixes (`clip`, `t`, `word`, …), bare commands, module detail, `proj` workbench commands.

## PR requirements

If adding home sections: update `LAUNCHER_HOME_CONSTRAINTS.md`, `UX_BEHAVIOR_RULES.md`, `MANUAL_QA_CHECKLIST.md`, and `LauncherHomeAggregatorTests`.
